# Brick Blitz — stable v1

`brick-blitz` is tagged `stable: 'v1'` in `src/platform/catalog.ts`. See `STABLE.md`.

## Do not change

Unless the user **explicitly authorizes** changes to Brick Blitz:

- Do not edit files under `src/games/brick-blitz/` or `games/brick-blitz/`
- Do not change ball physics, paddle movement, collision logic, brick breaking, power-ups, levels, or difficulty
- Do not change premium presentation (UI, graphics, audio, effects, HUD, menus) without authorization

## Frozen scope

- `src/games/brick-blitz/game.ts` — gameplay + canvas rendering
- `src/games/brick-blitz/main.ts` — bootstrap, HUD wiring
- `src/games/brick-blitz/bbAudio.ts` — premium SFX
- `src/games/brick-blitz/style.css` — Ethio Telecom premium theme
- `games/brick-blitz/index.html` — menus, HUD, overlays

## Instead

- Copy Brick Blitz **patterns** into shared modules or other games
- Fix platform/hub/backend issues without touching Brick Blitz game code
- If a shared change affects Brick Blitz, **tell the user** which shared file changed and why
